    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125710/extras/91abc295ccebf4e7c2ecc4498e1890c2.avif?t=1740467039\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine it's YOU with YOUR FRIENDS who have to fight monsters and demons to save the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Fake Ducks: Spooky Chronicles” is a turn-based RPG inspired by the great classics and set in the modern day that is about just that!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It tells of the misadventures of a group of bizarre friends who, thanks to the powers gained from an ancient pendant, must prevent a mysterious individual from getting his hands on a dark talisman that could compromise the future of the world. There's just one problem... Let's just say that our friends are not the classic heroes expected to save the planet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So it's up to you to guide them to success amidst puzzles to solve and strange monsters to defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your skills and discover what lies behind the diabolical plan of the 'hooded man. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a full-fledged Fake Duck with &quot;Fake Ducks: Spooky Chronicles&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't be fake. Play Fake Ducks!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125710/extras/24d5c9c869043161d46dad81c7a30aa1.avif?t=1740467039\" width=616 height=230 /></span>Face hordes of strange enemies in turn-based combat with simple but strategic and often challenging mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125710/extras/59b7c72b9fae0243315c35d9da932feb.avif?t=1740467039\" width=616 height=230 /></span>A total of seven levels all to explore and complete, filled with puzzles, riddles, obstacles and hidden rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125710/extras/0c772564df09dece626dbd28551d109b.avif?t=1740467039\" width=616 height=230 /></span>Form your ideal team with your favorite Fake Ducks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125710/extras/1f16c2d6470d7e9cd58ab28a42913e5a.avif?t=1740467039\" width=616 height=230 /></span>Upgrade characters' abilities more and more through the rewards in each level.</p>",
